Add file /etc/apt/sources.list.d/econauten-deepamehta.list
 * deb http://www.econauten.de/deb/ trusty/

Add key:
 * curl -fsSL http://www.econauten.de/deb/gpg | sudo apt-key add -
 
Install deepamehta:
 * sudo apt update && sudo apt install deepamehta

Known Issues:

 * After a fresh installation or update you need to restart deepamehta a few times bfore it comes up properly.

Outlook:

 * A future version should come without adduser und perl-mosules depencies (deluser).


Juergen Neumann


